{"word":"G4868 - συναίρω - synaírō - soon-ah'-ee-ro - Reckon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναίρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synaírō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ah'-ee-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Reckon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கணக்குப்பார், கணக்குக்கேள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to take up together with another or others"},{"paragraph":"2. to bring together with others"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G142 - αἴρω - aírō - ah'-ee-ro/142\">G142</a>; to <i>make up together</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>compute</i> (an account): - reckon, take.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}